content:
function refuleAll()
    if (turtle.refuel()) then
        turtle.refuel()
    else
        return
    end
end


function stairs()

    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    turtle.digUp()
    turtle.up()
    turtle.digUp()
    turtle.up()
    turtle.turnRight()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    turtle.digDown()
    turtle.down()
    turtle.digDown()
    turtle.down()
    turtle.digDown()
    turtle.down()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    turtle.dig()
    turtle.forward()
    turtle.turnRight()
    
end
